# A React component in 10 declarative lines. The widget primitives
# below (`heading_for`, `button_inc`, `paragraph_when_not`) are
# ABSTRACT — no JSX in the source — so the same script could target
# Vue or Svelte by swapping the library.

component Counter
    prop label string
    prop initial int

    state count int 0
    state hidden bool false

    heading_for label count
    button_inc "+1" count
    button_toggle "Toggle" hidden
    paragraph_when_not hidden "visible"
end
